      "text": "このバラエティ番組の台本は……もういらないわよね\n事務所で処分してもらわないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This variety show script… I guess I don't need it anymore.\nI should ask the office to dispose of it for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
