      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.3666679383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、それ……捨てちゃうならもらえませんか？\nついでに……出来れば、その、サインも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ if you're throwing that away… could I have it?\nAnd if possible… um‚ your signature too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.933334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいわよ。ふふ、雫のアイドル好きはさすがね\n……はい、どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind. Hehe‚ your love for idols is impressive as always.\n…Here you go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.933334605,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
