          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6433.3320617
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.8666679383
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.5666679383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぉぉ……！　ありがとうございます……！\n大切にします……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoaaa…! Thank you so much…!\nI'll cherish it forever…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.8666667938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "（星見プロにきてから、いろんな子から慕って）\n（もらえるようになったわよね。ふふ、悪くないわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Since coming to Hoshimi Pro‚ many girls have come to)\n(look up to me. Hehe‚ it's not so bad.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8666667938,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9200.001271600002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "この手袋、さすがに古くなってきたわね\n新しいのも買ったし、そろそろ処分しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These gloves have definitely seen better days.\nI bought a new pair‚ so it's time to get rid of these.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5666680654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "その手袋、捨てちゃうならもらってもいいですか？\nあと、せっかくだからサインを……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those gloves‚ if you're throwing them away‚ may I have them?\nOh‚ and since you're at it‚ your signature…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1333367666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　もう古いし、やめといた方がいいと思うけど……\nというか、ただの手袋になんでサインを……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? They're already worn out‚ I don't think you'd want them…\nAnyway‚ why would you want a signature on plain gloves?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2000044506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "このクッキー、美味しいわね。個別の包装になってて\n食べたい分だけ食べれるところも気に入ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These cookies are delicious. I like how they're individually\nwrapped so I can eat just as many as I want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4000052136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、そのクッキーの袋もらってもいいですか？\nあとサインして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ could I have that cookie wrapper?\nAnd please sign it for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6000052136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "え……これ、ただのゴミよ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… this is just literal trash‚ you know?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4666606905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0499950411
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "かなりデータが揃ってきた。台本の書き込みのクセ……\n好きな色、好きな味……ここから考察出来ることは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've gathered quite a bit of data. Script-writing habits…\nFavorite colors‚ favorite flavors… What I can deduce from this is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0999950411,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16166.6704812
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.1666617078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "データが多ければ多いほど、考察がはかどる……！\nああ、苦しい、しんどい……本当にありがとう……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more data I have‚ the more my deductions flow smoothly…!\nAh‚ it's so overwhelming‚ so intense… Thank you so much…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1666617078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.1666617078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、何やってるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ what exactly are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1666617078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6333299003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "ハッ！　莉央さんっ！？\nな、なな、な、なぜここに！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gah! Rio-san!?\nW-W-W-Why are you here?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6333299003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.200008774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに怪しいからつけてきたのよ……\nはぁ……ゴミからの考察って、探偵か何かなの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you were acting suspicious‚ so I followed you…\nSigh… Deducing things from trash? Are you a detective or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.200008774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.700008774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい。私、小学生の頃からリズノワの\nファンだから、もっと莉央さんのことを知りたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm sorry. I've been a fan of LizNoir since elementary\nschool‚ so I wanted to know more about you‚ Rio-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.700008774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9000199638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、一度は「あげる」って言ったものだけど……\n今後は普通に聞いてちょうだい。知りたいことは話すわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I did say you could have those things‚ but…\nFrom now on‚ just ask me normally. I'll tell you what you want to know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9000199638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.2000199638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_05-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、考察するのも楽しいから\nなかなかやめられなさそう――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But deducing things is so much fun\nI don't think I can easily stop――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2000199638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
